===Etymology===
From Greek.

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-system.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[collection]] of [[organized]] things; as, a [[solar system]].
# A [[way]] of [[organising]] or [[planning]].
# A [[whole]] [[composed]] of [[relationship]]s among the [[member]]s.
# In music, a set of [[staff]]s that indicate [[instrument]]s or [[sound]]s that are to be played [[simultaneously]].

